summary: Killing Eve s2 thought... [spoiler][[MORE]] I’m sure I’m not the only one, but I think that the scenes in the s2 bts photos of...
body:
Killing Eve s2 thought… [spoiler]

I’m sure I’m not the only one, but I think that the scenes in the s2 bts photos of Konstantin and Villanelle are flashbacks. This is because in ep8 of s1, after Villanelle shoots Konstantin… The next scene shows Eve, Kenny and Carolyn sitting at the airport. Carolyn gets a short phone call and when she hangs up Kenny [I think] says “Konstantin?” and Carolyn replies with “I’m afraid so.” Eve then replies to that with “There goes that lead”. So to me it sounds like he had died based on Eve’s response.
